{"text_id":131262,"tokens":["In"," recent"," years",","," there"," has"," been"," a"," growing"," debate"," over"," whether"," schools"," should"," allow"," students"," to"," design"," their"," own"," summer"," projects"," or"," if"," teachers"," should"," continue"," to"," assign"," predetermined"," projects","."," While"," both"," approaches"," have"," their"," merits",","," I"," argue"," that"," giving"," students"," the"," freedom"," to"," choose"," their"," own"," projects"," is"," the"," better"," option","."," This"," approach"," not"," only"," motivates"," students"," and"," accommodates"," individual"," learning"," styles",","," but"," it"," also"," promotes"," a"," sense"," of"," ownership"," and"," responsibility"," that"," is"," crucial"," for"," continued"," learning",".","\n\n","On"," the"," one"," hand",","," teacher","-","designed"," summer"," projects"," offer"," several"," benefits","."," Teachers"," can"," ensure"," that"," the"," projects"," align"," with"," the"," curriculum"," and"," learning"," objectives",","," which"," helps"," to"," maintain"," a"," consistent"," level"," of"," academic"," rigor","."," This"," approach"," also"," minimizes"," scheduling"," conflicts"," and"," ensures"," that"," all"," students"," are"," working"," on"," similar"," topics",","," making"," it"," easier"," for"," teachers"," to"," provide"," support"," and"," guidance",".","\n\n","However",","," teacher","-","designed"," projects"," can"," also"," be"," limiting"," and"," demo","tiv","ating"," for"," students","."," When"," students"," are"," given"," a"," predetermined"," project",","," they"," may"," not"," feel"," a"," sense"," of"," ownership"," or"," investment"," in"," the"," work","."," Additionally",","," a"," one","-","size","-","fits","-","all"," approach"," does"," not"," take"," into"," account"," individual"," learning"," styles"," or"," interests","."," Some"," students"," may"," thrive"," in"," a"," more"," structured"," environment",","," while